item.title: Resources
item.description: Join conversations with the other people who are involved in the creation, maintenance, and future of open-cluster-management. We want to hear from you. How you are using open-cluster-management? What we can do to make it better? To understand how the Open Cluster Management community is governed, visit the Community repo. Get Connected See the following options to connect with the community: GitHub Mailing group Slack Community meetings
